  "title": "IT Manager-POS System",
  "description": "<p><strong>Benefits of joining us:</strong></p><p>•        Performance related pay;</p><p>•        Salary increment;</p><p>•        2% Medical Allowance</p><p><strong>Job Descriptions：</strong></p><p>•        Lead a cross-functional team to deliver POS projects efficiently, maintaining high standards and timely outcomes.</p><p>•        Gather feedback from clients and end-users to guide system improvements and enhance usability, performance, and reliability.</p><p>•        Translate product strategy and market requirements into technical solutions that drive adoption and competitiveness.</p><p>•        Plan and manage system updates and feature releases, ensuring smooth deployment and alignment with business needs.</p><p>•        Support ongoing product development to drive user growth, improve market performance, and achieve business objectives</p><p><strong>Job Requirements：</strong></p><p>•        Degree in Computer Science, Software Engineering, Information Systems, or other related fields.</p><p>•        Proven experience in POS system development, deployment, optimisation, and maintenance.</p><p>•        Experience in POS, retail, F&B, or payment industries, with hands-on knowledge of product rollout.</p><p>•        Strong leadership skills, with the ability to manage cross-functional teams and deliver results.</p><p>•        Self-motivated, outcome-focused, and able to thrive under pressure, with a clear focus on business impact and user value.<br /></p><p>Maxhunt Resource Pte Ltd | EA Licence: 22C1322<br />\nCynthia Lai | Registration No: R25146301</p>",
